Create a Mesh.

[ Noise Texture ]
Scale 3.000
Detail 15.000
Rough. 0.5
Distortion 0
FAC <--> VALUE [ Map Range ]

[ Map Range ]
RESULT <---> FAC [ Color Ramp ]

[ Color Ramp ]
Keep default Black and White!
Arrows, black at "R" (RGB) and white at "L" (Linear)
COLOR > DENSITY [ Principled Volume ]

[ Principled Volume ]
VOLUME <---> VOLUME [ Material Output ]

Tip: Put a light source behind to set color of this cloud/fog on a better and natural way, even if white one!
